## Summary

*This summary is not part of the license. It grants nothing, and it is not a
promise. It is here so you can tell in ten seconds whether you owe money. If it
disagrees with the terms below, the terms below win.*

- The source is public, and you can read it, change it, and run it. This is a
  **source-available** license, not an open source license.
- If your company has **fewer than 10 people** — employees and contractors,
  counted across every affiliate — you may use, change, and self-host the
  software for free, in production, including commercially.
- **10 or more people means you need a paid commercial license.** Email
  support@exponential.at.
- **Anyone, at any size,** may use the software for free for evaluation,
  development, testing, and non-commercial research or education.
- **Nobody may resell the software to others as a hosted or managed service**,
  however small they are.

